    "As mentioned in Section I-A, in the context of this project with ÖPAG, the input NL requirements, glossary terms and domain-information corpus are written in a mix of German and English languages, while TS-related information is in English.",
    "Prompt GenerationThis step takes as input a set of NL requirements, an example TS and a brief description of the TS that needs to be generated.",
    "Providing the example TS is optional.",
    "However, as we argue in Section IV, providing the example yields better results.",
    "The output of the step is a prompt which is passed onto the next steps."
